  },

  methods: {
    changeIndex(num) {
      if (this.myIndex >= 0 && this.myIndex < this.typeProducts.length) this.myIndex += num;
    },

    changePage(page) {
      this.myIndex = page;
    },

    addToCart(id) {
      axios.get(`http://localhost:8081/api/cart/add/${id}/qty/`);
      store.state.cartAmount += 1;
      this.$swal("CMA", "成功加入購物車", "success");
    }

  },
  computed: {
    typeProducts() {
      if (this.msg === "全部商品") {
        return this.products;
      } else {
        return this.products.filter(item => {
          return item.productCatalog === this.msg;
        });
      }
    }

  }
